        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued May 1 at 6:27PM CDT until May 1 at 7:15PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>SVRAMA

The National Weather Service in Amarillo has issued a

* Severe Thunderstorm Warning for...
Central Dallam County in the Panhandle of Texas...

* Until 715 PM CDT.

* At 627 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 11 miles northwest
of Ware, or 22 miles east of Clayton, moving southeast at 20 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and nickel size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to roofs, siding, and trees is possible.

* This severe thunderstorm will remain over mainly rural areas of
central Dallam County.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
